reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very happy with this purchase! Everything came very well packaged and the instructions were easy to understand. Assembly was 45 minutes total from start to finish. Feels very solid and sturdy and the wood is beautiful! Great value for the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High quality, easy assembly!
reviews.reviewText: I never write reviews, but I am blown away by this bed frame. Immediately upon delivery, I was impressed by how well it was packaged and how gorgeous the wood is in person. It’s stunning and shows zero signs of damage or flaws from shipping. Assembly took me less than an hour, and I did this by myself as a 35 year old woman, without any need for additional tools. Everything was easily identifiable through the instructions and the parts fit perfectly.I also bought the matching bedside tables and the whole set up is gorgeous!10/10

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: We were looking for a platform frame in a natural finish with clean lines AND we were working on a budget so we were really excited to find this bed. It's a king so I definitely needed help to build it, but assembly was extremely easy. Holes were all drilled properly and all dowels are very secure. It was packed very well, no damage to any of the wood, and it just looks absolutely perfect in our room. The slats are even with the frame, so the mattress doesn't drop down at all to keep it in place but ours doesn't move around at all so not an issue to me, you really only see it when the bed isn't made. It's a gamble to order furniture online because you never know what condition it will arrive in, but again the producer did a great job packing and protecting the pieces which was a huge relief! Would definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This frame was very easy to assemble. All the holes lined up, and the frame is incredibly sturdy. It has a very beautiful aesthetic. The height is slightly taller than I expected, which was a very pleasant surprise! I am very happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super easy to assemble! Even by yourself
reviews.reviewText: I liked how easy assembly was it was very easy to understand even without the instructions. It’s sturdy and lovely! So glad I bought it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good product, hard to match color with different furniture
reviews.reviewText: Sturdy and good bed frame. Pain in the butt to screw in bolts. Its design is just pain.. to set up. It does squeak tho... nice looking bed frame.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Solid. Good instruction. Easy assembly.
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Packaging was very good. All parts present with spares. Assembly allen wrench had ball end for easy reach on the angle required. Numbered stickers for parts end up being hidden after assembly. Best of all after reading all the reviews from 1 to 5 rating we encountered none of the problems that others had. The bed is solid and looks very nice. I would suggest being careful when torquing the bolts based on other reviews. Snug plus 1/2 turn was my method and it seemed adequate. When we rotate the mattress in the future I will check for bolt tightness. Overall a solid frame and easy and well written assembly process/instruction makes this a good consideration.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Love the style of this frame, seems strong! Assembly was fairly easy
